# 🚀 Overview

AgriChain Pro is a modern AI-powered agriculture supply chain platform designed to connect:

* 🚜 Farmers
* 🚚 Transporters
* 🏪 Vendors

The platform helps optimize agricultural logistics, crop management, inventory tracking, AI-based recommendations, and smart transportation workflows.

This project combines a premium SaaS-style frontend with a Flask + MongoDB backend architecture.

---

# ✨ Features

## 🔐 Authentication System

* User Signup & Login
* Secure Password Hashing using bcrypt
* MongoDB User Storage
* Session Management using Local Storage
* Profile Avatar Upload
* Dynamic User Dropdown
* Logout Animation

